name: FormulaOneSeason
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: formula one season
des:
This skill informs you about the current formula one season and is optimized for Echo Show/Spot.

You can ask for:
- drivers
- teams
- a country to get the race result
- race calendar
- next race and last race
- champion

It is an unofficial skill and has no connection to the organizer or teams.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
